title: @MMathisLab import deeplabcut error
body:
Hello, so I was having the same problem as xcccc402 and I followed the below advice to try to solve it

xcccc402, the first part of this answer from @MMathisLab should help you:
> So, the solution is as follows:
> 
> (1) install the base code by:
> 
> `git clone https://github.com/AlexEMG/DeepLabCut`
> 
> cd into DeepLabCut
> 
> Then run:
> 
> ```
> import deeplabcut
> 
> deeplabcut.__version__
> 
> deeplabcut.__file__ 
> ```

_Originally posted by @jeylau in https://github.com/DeepLabCut/DeepLabCut/issues/611#issuecomment-602828438_

Now whenever I try to use command import deeplabcut I get the following error:
